nic_groups_in_the_United_States_by_household_income#Asian_Americans">收入超过美国几乎所有其他族裔这一</a>事实就证明了这一点</p><p>然而，尽管有这些天然优势，巴基斯坦仍然是世界上最大的经济困境之一。这是一个贫穷的国家，收入增长非常缓慢；尽管一开始要富裕得多，但现在已经被印度和孟加拉国放弃了： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0670a993-a466-49c3-b6f8-a46d29f309cf_1360x971.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0670a993-a466-49c3-b6f8-a46d29f309cf_1360x971.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0670a993-a466-49c3-b6f8-a46d29f309cf_1360x971.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0670a993-a466-49c3-b6f8-a46d29f309cf_1360x971.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0670a993-a466-49c3-b6f8-a46d29f309cf_1360x971.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0670a993-a466-49c3-b6f8-a46d29f309cf_1360x971.jpeg" width="1360" height="971" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0670a993-a466-49c3-b6f8-a46d29f309cf_1360x971.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quo