基金组织本身的钱。该组织可能不太愿意借钱给巴基斯坦来偿还<em>中国</em>债务，因为这将使中国政府完整，同时让国际货币基金组织承担责任。中国不太可能像国际货币基金组织那样向巴基斯坦提供无休止的救助。</p><p>正如巴基斯坦裔美国经济学家<a href="https://twitter.com/AtifRMian/status/1756790439787594026">阿蒂夫·米安所说</a>，“这个国家已经破产了。”</p><p>这意味着巴基斯坦面临着一场典型的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/pakistan-is-in-big-trouble">新兴市场货币危机</a>的更大危险，在这种危机中，一个国家的货币变得如此便宜，以至于偿还外债的唯一方法要么是违约，要么是高通胀——这两种方式都会损害巴基斯坦的利益。实体经济很多。巴基斯坦卢比已经大幅贬值： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F885afe6e-2a2f-475b-993c-db847e2fcf98_1347x529.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F885afe6e-2a2f-475b-993c-db847e2fcf98_1347x529.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F885afe6e-2a2f-475b-993c-db847e2fcf98_1347x529.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F885afe6e-2a2f-475b-993c-db847e2fcf98_1347x529.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F885afe6e-2a2f-475b-993c-db847e2fcf98_1347x529.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F885afe6e-2a2f-475b-993c-db847e2fcf98_1347x529.jpeg" width="1347" height="529" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot