京本人的政治压力。普京将法律和秩序作为他的政府和 2000 年代言论的关键主题；这大概会导致公共安全有所改善，但也可能会激励全国各地的警察部门表现出虚假的进步。</p><p>联合国和世界银行对此表示同意。他们的统计数据显示，俄罗斯的凶杀率大幅下降，但到 2021 年仅降至每 10 万人中 7 人左右： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg" width="916" height="779" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/163fc2d1-d4f4-4b81-80db-cc2e08432e83_916x779.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:779,&quot;width&quot;:916,&quot;resizeW