A bunch of handy charts about climate changeA couple dozen pictures are worth a couple thousand words. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-bunch-of-handy-charts-about-climate https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-bunch-of-handy-charts-about-climateNoah Smith Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:08:52 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F988526b2-9e0b-40ed-a728-4410a2e4c424_748x369.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F988526b2-9e0b-40ed-a728-4410a2e4c424_748x369.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F988526b2-9e0b-40ed-a728-4410a2e4c424_748x369.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F988526b2-9e0b-40ed-a728-4410a2e4c424_748x369.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F988526b2-9e0b-40ed-a728-4410a2e4c424_748x369.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F988526b2-9e0b-40ed-a728-4410a2e4c424_748x369.jpeg" width="748" height="369" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/988526b2-9e0b-40ed-a728-4410a2e4c424_748x369.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&