能和电池的魔力，我们可以保持文明的进步嗡嗡作响，同时还可以减少对地球气候的破坏性影响。是的，那里仍然有一些大障碍 - 中东煤炭行业，中东大肆宣传，美国的nimbys等等。但是与15年前形成鲜明对比的是，我们现在拥有完成工作的工具。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-bunch-of-handy-charts-about-climate?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-bunch-of-handy-charts-about-climate?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p>; 
