Do poor countries need a new development strategy?Bangladesh and Southeast Asia are defying the economists who say industrialization is dead. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/do-poor-countries-need-a-new开发https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/do-poor-countries-need-a-new开发Noah SmithThu, 08 Feb 2024 10:33:53 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F613a14af-627a-42b6-afc2-4be8608a36d3_1618x894.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F613a14af-627a-42b6-afc2-4be8608a36d3_1618x894.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F613a14af-627a-42b6-afc2-4be8608a36d3_1618x894.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F613a14af-627a-42b6-afc2-4be8608a36d3_1618x894.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F613a14af-627a-42b6-afc2-4be8608a36d3_1618x894.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F613a14af-627a-42b6-afc2-4be8608a36d3_1618x894.jpeg" width="714" height="394.2692307692308" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/613a14af-627a-42b6-afc2-4be8608a36